I Can Cook is a children's television series, that was broadcast on CBeebies, from October 2009 to December 2012.  It was presented by Katy Ashworth, who demonstrates how to prepare and cook simple dishes, while entertaining with songs.(https://www.bbc.co.uk/cbeebies/icancook/ I Can Cook Official Microsite  Each show focuses on the creation of one dish, either savoury or sweet.
